    "CVCS was also generated using GTAV.",
    "It contains 280,000 images with a resolution of 1920 × 1080 pixels, obtained from 31 locations, with 60 to 120 different views for each location.",
    "Each image contains 90 to 180 pedestrians.",
    "This data set was generated by selecting two sets of parameters.",
    "First, scene-related features were chosen, i.e., location, ROI, weather conditions, 3D human models, etc."
